WindwardRestApi.Model

Class Xml_10DataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • WindwardRestApi.Model.DataSource
      • WindwardRestApi.Model.Xml_10DataSource

  • public class Xml_10DataSource
extends DataSource
    An XML 1.0 (.Net runtime) datasource to apply to a template. This can include datasets built from this datasource. Used as part of a document generation request. We strongly recommend you use Xml_20DataSource instead.
